    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to a type of travertine that is beige, cream, honey, and/or gold in color; it is lighter in color than barco.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
